snippet.title: Jason Momoa Finally Reveals He Dislikes Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Jason Momoa Finally Reveals He Dislikes Amber Heard
Amber Heard was sacked from Aquaman 2 for a reason, according to Jason Momoa. Jason Mamoa is a name that has been making waves in the entertainment industry for quite some time. Indeed, with the release of Aquaman earlier this year, he was the talk of Hollywood, and he was given the opportunity to portray a variety of parts in several films, leading us to wonder. When we next see this heartthrob on the big screen, it will be in 2022, thanks to Aquaman's massive popularity immediately after its debut.
